===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Hilda (Masters)}}
Hilda, who is based on the [[Battle Subway]] partner, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Tepig}} and its evolved forms {{p|Pignite}} and {{p|Emboar}}, along with {{p|Diancie}}, {{Shiny}} {{p|Grapploct}}, {{p|Victini}}, {{p|Leafeon}}, {{form|Tornadus|Incarnate Forme}} {{p|Tornadus}}, {{p|Iron Leaves}}, and {{p|Mienfoo}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Her Diancie is capable of [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolving]]. Hilda became a playable sync pair on September 30, 2019.

Hilda first appeared as an NPC during the eighteenth chapter of the [[PML arc]]. She also made a notable appearance later in the [[villain arc]]. 

